{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_11_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央 3話 トップアイドルのマネージャーさん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――現在",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は、本当にありがとう。まさか、葵の衣装まで\n用意してくれていたとはね。当日の朝、聞いて驚いたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much back then. I never imagined you’d even prepare Aoi’s outfit.\nI was surprised when I heard about it on the morning of the event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "貴方のおかげで、四人揃って\nセミファイナルの舞台に立つことが出来た",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to you‚ the four of us\nwere able to stand on the stage for the semifinals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.3365303993
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、何も出来ないとか、何も力になれないなんて\nそんなバカなこと、二度と言わないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So don’t ever say something foolish like\n“I couldn’t do anything” or “I couldn’t help.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.2262637485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。もう言いませんよ\nそれにしても約束、本当に果たしちゃいましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes. I won’t say it again.\nStill‚ you really kept your promise‚ didn’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2262637485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、貴方をトップアイドルのマネージャーにする\nっていう約束？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you mean the promise to make you\nthe manager of a top idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4837188721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4はVENUSプログラムの頂点に立つアイドル\nそういう意味では、約束を果たしたと言えるのかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "BIG4 are the idols at the top of the VENUS program.\nIn that sense‚ you could say the promise has been fulfilled.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7205469447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.3928145407
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "でも……考えてみたの。私達にとっての頂点――\nトップアイドルは、ランキング一位に立つこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I thought about it. For us‚ the pinnacle—\nbeing a top idol means reaching number one in the rankings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.6170550029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私達LizNoirの\nトップアイドルへの道のりは、まだこれからよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ for us‚ LizNoir’s journey\nto becoming top idols is still ahead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3503883362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.142313798
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "今度はサニピや月ストとも戦わないとね。また勝っても\n負けても、貴方を複雑な気分にさせちゃうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next‚ we have to compete with Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest.\nWhether we win or lose‚ I wonder if it’ll make you feel conflicted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7503863017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはそうなんですけど……勘弁して下さいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah‚ that’s true… but please‚ give me a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.7109078405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.0029681998
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、貴方が約束を果たしたと思っているなら……\nそうね、気の利いたプレゼントでも用意すれば？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if you feel like you’ve fulfilled your promise…\nThen maybe you should prepare a thoughtful present?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0488638242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　プレゼントですか？　たとえばどんな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? A present? Like‚ what kind of…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1074573356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.2077975749
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "それくらい自分で考えなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should think of that yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2077975749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "大体「何をプレゼントしてほしいんですか」って\n直接聞くような人は、モテないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "People who directly ask “What do you want as a gift?”\naren’t very popular‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.328954665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.9885458627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "て、手厳しいですね……分かりました。考えておきます\n……おっと、そろそろ撮影本番ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-that’s harsh… okay‚ I’ll think about it.\n…Oh‚ it’s almost time for the shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.7666615803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.4057803791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、それじゃ行ってくるわ\nプレゼント、楽しみにしてるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I’ll go now.\nI’ll be looking forward to your present.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4057803791,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4478.841814900008,
          "startTime": 117.884622194
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.6012888589
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.6012888589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "撮影お疲れ様でした、莉央さん\n相変わらず、手際がいいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work on the shoot‚ Rio-san.\nAs always‚ you’re very efficient.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.0622184752
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "いつも通りよ。それに葵の撮影がもう終わってるから\nスタッフさん達も手慣れているわ。そのおかげよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As usual. Besides‚ Aoi’s shoot is already done.\nThe staff are experienced‚ too. That helps a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.5564595224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.1930410701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "この後、撮影した映像のチェックがあるから\n貴方も付き合ってちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll be reviewing the footage later‚ so—\nI want you to come along as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.5897989592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "おぉ……カッコいい。やっぱり絵になるな\nまるでゲームのラスボスみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… so cool. Truly a picture-perfect scene.\nLike the final boss in a video game.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.7333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待って。それ、アイドルに対する誉め言葉？\n強そうとか、怖いってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a minute. Is that a compliment for an idol?\nYou mean I look strong or intimidating?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.5740847272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ、そうじゃなくて、迫力があるというか\n……そうだ！　女王様とか、将軍みたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ not exactly‚ more like… powerful presence.\n…Right! Like a queen or a general.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.2666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "……それ、フォローしてるつもりなの？\nまぁいいわ。的外れって訳じゃないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Are you trying to cover yourself with that?\nWell‚ it’s fine. Not entirely off the mark.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.7568947476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "実は、衣装デザイナーさんと話し合って決めた\nこの衣装に込めたテーマはね、『戦い』なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ when we discussed with the costume designer‚\nthe theme we put into this outfit was “battle.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.0235593797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "いつだったか、さくらに聞かれたわ\n「あなたにとって、アイドルってなんですか？」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One day‚ Sakura asked me—\n“What is idol to you?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.823572604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "私の答えは……『戦い』だった\n自分の願いを叶えるために、戦いに身を投じる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My answer was… “battle.”\nThrowing yourself into battle to achieve your own dreams—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.3235705694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "そうやって生きていくこと、そのものが\n私にとっては『アイドル』なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "living that way itself\nis the meaning of \"idol\" to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.8235837937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
