      "text": "決勝トーナメントの間、弱い私の気持ちは\n何度も揺らいでしまったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "During the finals‚ my weak feelings\nwavered many times‚ but—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.2580382984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "そのたびにこの衣装が、私に覚悟を――\n『アイドル』とはなんなのかを、思い出させてくれた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "each time‚ this outfit reminded me of my resolve‚\nand what it truly means to be an “idol.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.1246958097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
